### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082/api/v1
@bookingId = 27
@apartmentsApiUrl = http://localhost:8081/api/v1

### 1. Crear reserva pública (sin user_id) - Usando apartment_id específico
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apartment_id": 16,
  "user_info": {
    "first_name": "Laura",
    "last_name": "Esteven",
    "dni": "36763321",
    "phone": "+5491156321456",
    "email": "laura.esteven@example.com"
  },
  "check_in": "2026-01-11",
  "check_out": "2026-01-15",
  "guests": 2,
  "payment_method": "transferencia"
}

### 1b. Crear reserva pública - Usando apartment_type (asignación automática)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apartment_type": "double_matrimonial",
  "user_info": {
    "first_name": "Valeria",
    "last_name": "Ulises",
    "dni": "23677332",
    "phone": "+5491179234299",
    "email": "valeria.ulises@example.com"
  },
  "check_in": "2026-01-28",
  "check_out": "2026-01-29",
  "guests": 2,
  "payment_method": "transferencia"
}

### 2. Crear reserva como admin para un usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apartment_id": 17,
  "user_id": 1,
  "user_info": {
    "first_name": "Angie",
    "last_name": "Yunes",
    "dni": "46987432",
    "phone": "+5491198765110",
    "email": "angie.yunes@example.com"
  },
  "check_in": "2026-01-05",
  "check_out": "2026-01-10",
  "guests": 2,
  "payment_method": "transferencia"
}

### 3. Obtener todas las reservas (para admin) - NUEVO
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?size=100

### 3a. Obtener todas las reservas con filtros
# GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?apartment_id=15&status=confirmed&size=50

### 4. Obtener reserva por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}

### 5. Obtener reservas por usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/user/1

### 6. Actualizar reserva (cambiar fecha)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "check_in": "2025-11-21",
  "check_out": "2025-11-25"
}

### 7. Cancelar reserva
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "cancelled"
}

### 8. Eliminar reserva
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}

### 9. Crear reserva que fallará por disponibilidad (fechas solapadas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apartment_type": "quadruple",
